# Collections Feature Visual Redesign -- Implementation Plan

## Overview

This plan covers a complete visual overhaul of the Collections feature across 7 JSX components and 1 CSS file (1245 lines). The work is organized into 6 sequential phases, ordered so that foundational changes land first and dependent changes follow naturally.

---

## PHASE 1: CSS Variable Migration + Typography (Foundation)

**Rationale**: Every subsequent phase depends on the design token system being in place. This is a pure CSS pass with zero JSX changes, making it safe and sweeping.

